  $
  overline(x)_"甲" &= (32000 + 55000 + 45000 + 40000 + 37000) / (5) &= 41800 \
  overline(x)_"乙" &= (38000+52000+50000+47000+35000) / (5) &= 44400
  $

  Obviously, $overline(x)_"乙" > overline(x)_"甲"$, and therefore 乙公司 is higher.
]

